==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Anchor space
<hw>Anchor space</hw>. <fld>(Billiards)</fld> <def>In the balk-line
game, any of eight spaces, 7 inches by 3⟦frac12⟧, lying along a cushion
and bisected transversely by a balk line. Object balls in an anchor
space are treated as in balk.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Anchor watch</ent>⟦br⟧
